column5: Hello all,  Got introduced to the site from Nipfisher from the OOD forum and thought I would join!  I am an avid hard water angler and have been doing it for over 20 years. I generally fish Nipissing, Quinte and Simcoe for the most part and I mostly target walleye. I usually get out 8-10 times a season and enjoy taking my family for several of those outings. We are from the Grand Valley, ON area and we also do a lot of hunting for Turkey, deer and waterfowl.  Looking forward to the conversations and new friendships in the near future!  Cheers,  East Luther (Jay)
Welcome aboard the board, Jay. Looking forward to reading of your adventures.
